column5: Say hello to my first Muskie!  We were targeting walleye and this beast smashed my Livetarget jointed smelt.
always change up your hooks and split rings with any Live Target bait if your going to chase fish that actually pull (ie, pike, muskie, salmon, trout, etc).  Super nice fish!!!

Thanks guys!   always change up your hooks and split rings with any Live Target bait if your going to chase fish that actually pull (ie, pike, muskie, salmon, trout, etc).  Super nice fish!!!  I don't fish with Livetarget much but I guess they're the same as Rapala.    so are you addicted now?   It was a bad ass fight but I wish I could've seen the jumps, It jumped multiple times.  I hope to slowly get a musky setup by next year.
she's a beaut for sure....better than my first!
Hell of a start, nice dark fish too!
The downward decline begins. Welcome to the club.
empty pockets and minds full of hope lol
Very nice fish - especially for your first!
Wow, nice fish.   I'm still holding off on the musky thing.
I thought you were one of the guys from Slip Knot there for a minute, with your wardrobe, almost crapped myself
I got invited to fish for Musky tomorrow but I had to decline because I don't have the gear
